     H            Y.
     F** ADKR92 **********************************
     F*パラメータの日付以降の確定発注を検索    *
     F*     KATOGI.     2015.12.16               *
     F********************************************
     FAH#PL14 IF  E           K        DISK
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80WKZEHZ
     I                                        1   40WKZEYY
     I                                        5   60WKZEMM
     I                                        7   80WKZEDD
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80WKTOHZ
     I                                        1   40WKTOYY
     I                                        5   60WKTOMM
     I                                        7   80WKTODD
      *
     I           SDS
     I                                      254 263 @@USER
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           P1SHN1  5
     C                     PARM           P1SHN2  5
     C                     PARM           P1SHN3  2
     C                     PARM           P1ZEHZ  80
     C                     PARM           P1TOBI  20
     C                     PARM           P9MAIS  50
      *
     C                     Z-ADDP1ZEHZ    WKZEHZ
      *
     C           KEY1      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           #KSHN1  5
     C                     KFLD           #KSHN2  5
     C                     KFLD           #KSHN3  2
     C                     KFLD           #KHTYY  40
     C                     KFLD           #KHTMM  20
     C                     KFLD           #KHTDD  20
     C                     KFLD           #KHTBB  20
     C           KEY2      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           #KSHN1  5
     C                     KFLD           #KSHN2  5
     C                     KFLD           #KSHN3  2
     C                     MOVELP1SHN1    #KSHN1
     C                     MOVELP1SHN2    #KSHN2
     C                     MOVELP1SHN3    #KSHN3
     C                     Z-ADDWKZEYY    #KHTYY
     C                     Z-ADDWKZEMM    #KHTMM
     C                     Z-ADDWKZEDD    #KHTDD
     C                     Z-ADDP1TOBI    #KHTBB
     C                     Z-ADD0         P9MAIS
      *パラメータの日付・便でセットして
      *それ以降を品番で読む
     C           KEY1      SETLLAH#PL141
     C           KEY2      READEAH#PL141                 80
     C           *IN80     DOWEQ'0'
     C           CFSKJY    IFEQ 'D'
     C           CFSKHZ    ANDLE*DATE
     C                     ELSE
     C                     ADD  CFMAIS    P9MAIS
     C                     ENDIF
     C           KEY2      READEAH#PL141                 80
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
